{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/what-is-psychological-first-aid-and-how-to-apply-it/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ramonmorcillo.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"23efa917-1b89-5aac-a945-537dbe368d9f","excerpt":"Just as there is the Physical First Aid technique that we all have seen or heard about, there is also a psychological one not so well known. It could be said that it is just as important as the first one. As a way to introduce this topic and without going deeper into it a simple comparison could be that unlike Physical First Aid, in the psychological one, you don’t wait for an ambulance to arrive. For this reading, I structured the content in a basic problem-solving way based on the principle of the Five Ws. Table of Contents What is Psychological First Aid When to apply it How to apply it Why apply it Conclusions Resources What is Psychological First Aid  Psychological First Aid is a technique used with people who have just suffered the impact of tragic news, an accident, or have experienced a catastrophe. People who are in shock and feel vulnerable. They are trying to understand what has happened to them and the consequences of it. When to apply it  It is indicated to apply it from immediately after the impact of what has happened until approximately 72 hours later. This does not mean that after 72 hours the affected do not need help, just that psychological first aid is the proper technique in the first 72 hours after the event. After a month after the incident, if the person has not recovered from his normal life, it is advisable to go to a doctor. How to apply it  Here are the 5 Psychological First Aid main steps. The details and applications of each one vary with the patient’s age; you don’t calm a baby the same way you do with a teenager or an old man. Anyway, the concept remains the same for any age. Contain. First, we have to give the person security, make them feel safe. The important point is to try to prevent the person’s emotions, fears, feelings from overflowing. Calm. Help the person relax speaking in a slow voice, trying to conduct yourself as calmly as possible, lowering our activation tone. We will never tell the person that everything will be better when calmed down because it may not be true. Inform. We will not inform the person until it is calmed. We should not explain or give more information than the needed or give morbid details of what has happened. The shorter an explanation is, the more security it will give. Listen to what the person tells us without judging and give it the importance it has. It is preferable, to tell them that you do not know something than to tell them something you are not sure which later may not be true…","html":"<p>Just as there is the <strong>Physical First Aid</strong> technique that we all have seen or heard about, there is also a <em>psychological</em> one not so well known. It could be said that it is just <strong>as important as the first one.</strong> As a way to introduce this topic and without going deeper into it a simple comparison could be that <em>unlike Physical First Aid, in the psychological one, you don’t wait for an ambulance to arrive.</em></p>\n<p>For this reading, I structured the content in a basic <em>problem-solving</em> way based on the principle of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Five_Ws\">Five Ws.</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Table-of-Contents\" style=\"position:relative;\">Table of Contents<a href=\"#Table-of-Contents\" aria-label=\"Table of Contents permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#What-is-Psychological-First-Aid\">What is Psychological First Aid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#When-to-apply-it\">When to apply it</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#How-to-apply-it\">How to apply it</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Why-apply-it\">Why apply it</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Conclusions\">Conclusions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Resources\">Resources</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"What-is-Psychological-First-Aid\" style=\"position:relative;\">What is Psychological First Aid<a href=\"#What-is-Psychological-First-Aid\" aria-label=\"What is Psychological First Aid permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/8f6c2941f81bfb5345c8ff3e22feedaa/acb04/the_new_universe_81_1964_klaus_burgle.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The New Universe  81, 1964, Klaus Bürgle.\"\n        title=\"The New Universe  81, 1964, Klaus Bürgle.\"\n        src=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/8f6c2941f81bfb5345c8ff3e22feedaa/b4294/the_new_universe_81_1964_klaus_burgle.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/8f6c2941f81bfb5345c8ff3e22feedaa/75985/the_new_universe_81_1964_klaus_burgle.jpg 150w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/8f6c2941f81bfb5345c8ff3e22feedaa/f93b5/the_new_universe_81_1964_klaus_burgle.jpg 300w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/8f6c2941f81bfb5345c8ff3e22feedaa/b4294/the_new_universe_81_1964_klaus_burgle.jpg 600w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/8f6c2941f81bfb5345c8ff3e22feedaa/acb04/the_new_universe_81_1964_klaus_burgle.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>The New Universe  81, 1964, Klaus Bürgle.</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>Psychological First Aid is a technique used with people who have just suffered the impact of tragic news, an accident, or have experienced a catastrophe.</strong> People who are in shock and feel vulnerable. They are trying to understand what has happened to them and the consequences of it.</p>\n<h2 id=\"When-to-apply-it\" style=\"position:relative;\">When to apply it<a href=\"#When-to-apply-it\" aria-label=\"When to apply it permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/a520e32f13102e0fb5ed1ec041d0e86b/acb04/suspension_railway_over_the_sahara_suspended_15_meters_high_the_world_of_tomorrow_birkel_scrapbook_1959_unknown_artist.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Suspension railway over the Sahara: suspended 15 meters high, The world of tomorrow, Birkel scrapbook, 1959, Unknown Artist.\"\n        title=\"Suspension railway over the Sahara: suspended 15 meters high, The world of tomorrow, Birkel scrapbook, 1959, Unknown Artist.\"\n        src=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/a520e32f13102e0fb5ed1ec041d0e86b/b4294/suspension_railway_over_the_sahara_suspended_15_meters_high_the_world_of_tomorrow_birkel_scrapbook_1959_unknown_artist.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/a520e32f13102e0fb5ed1ec041d0e86b/75985/suspension_railway_over_the_sahara_suspended_15_meters_high_the_world_of_tomorrow_birkel_scrapbook_1959_unknown_artist.jpg 150w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/a520e32f13102e0fb5ed1ec041d0e86b/f93b5/suspension_railway_over_the_sahara_suspended_15_meters_high_the_world_of_tomorrow_birkel_scrapbook_1959_unknown_artist.jpg 300w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/a520e32f13102e0fb5ed1ec041d0e86b/b4294/suspension_railway_over_the_sahara_suspended_15_meters_high_the_world_of_tomorrow_birkel_scrapbook_1959_unknown_artist.jpg 600w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/a520e32f13102e0fb5ed1ec041d0e86b/acb04/suspension_railway_over_the_sahara_suspended_15_meters_high_the_world_of_tomorrow_birkel_scrapbook_1959_unknown_artist.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Suspension railway over the Sahara: suspended 15 meters high, The world of tomorrow, Birkel scrapbook, 1959, Unknown Artist.</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>It is indicated to apply it <strong>from immediately after the impact of what has happened until approximately 72 hours later.</strong></p>\n<p>This does not mean that after 72 hours the affected do not need help, just that psychological first aid is the proper technique in the first 72 hours after the event.</p>\n<p>After a month after the incident, if the person has not recovered from his normal life, it is advisable to go to a doctor.</p>\n<h2 id=\"How-to-apply-it\" style=\"position:relative;\">How to apply it<a href=\"#How-to-apply-it\" aria-label=\"How to apply it permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 437px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/ac4859972f9d6fca8f0af8b81fd7d580/fca8a/the_new_universe_85_1968_klaus_burgle.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 129.99999999999997%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The New Universe 85, 1968,  Klaus Bürgle.\"\n        title=\"The New Universe 85, 1968,  Klaus Bürgle.\"\n        src=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/ac4859972f9d6fca8f0af8b81fd7d580/fca8a/the_new_universe_85_1968_klaus_burgle.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/ac4859972f9d6fca8f0af8b81fd7d580/75985/the_new_universe_85_1968_klaus_burgle.jpg 150w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/ac4859972f9d6fca8f0af8b81fd7d580/f93b5/the_new_universe_85_1968_klaus_burgle.jpg 300w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/ac4859972f9d6fca8f0af8b81fd7d580/fca8a/the_new_universe_85_1968_klaus_burgle.jpg 437w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>The New Universe 85, 1968,  Klaus Bürgle.</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Here are <strong>the 5 Psychological First Aid main steps.</strong> The details and applications of each one vary with the patient’s age; you don’t calm a baby the same way you do with a teenager or an old man. Anyway, the concept remains the same for any age.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Contain.</strong> First, we have to give the person security, <strong>make them feel safe.</strong> The important point is to try to prevent the person’s emotions, fears, feelings from overflowing.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Calm. Help the person relax</strong> speaking in a slow voice, trying to conduct yourself as calmly as possible, lowering our activation tone. We will never tell the person that everything will be better when calmed down because it may not be true.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Inform.</strong> We will not inform the person until it is calmed. We should not explain or give more information than the needed or give morbid details of what has happened. <strong>The shorter an explanation is, the more security it will give.</strong></p>\n<p>Listen to what the person tells us without judging and give it the importance it has. It is preferable, to tell them that you do not know something than to tell them something you are not sure which later may not be true.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Normalize.</strong> Normalize the symptoms and what is happening to the person. Make them see that they are not the only ones who have these feelings or reactions. <strong>Help them realize it is normal to experience those feelings.</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Comfort.</strong> Obviously, we have to <strong>comfort them and give them support.</strong> Try to make them feel useful. However, you have to accept that maybe you are not the one to comfort them the best. In this situation try to find the best way or person to comfort them.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"Why-apply-it\" style=\"position:relative;\">Why apply it<a href=\"#Why-apply-it\" aria-label=\"Why apply it permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/086f9/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"When a robot gets behind the wheel, 1974, Günter Radtke.\"\n        title=\"When a robot gets behind the wheel, 1974, Günter Radtke.\"\n        src=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/b4294/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/75985/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg 150w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/f93b5/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg 300w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/b4294/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg 600w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/8e1fc/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg 900w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/06891ca5ca6678f8104c81bd7eb0a251/086f9/when_a_robot_gets_behind_the_wheel_1974_gunter_radtke.jpg 973w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>When a robot gets behind the wheel, 1974, Günter Radtke.</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>Why apply it?</strong> There is no better reason than <strong>to help.</strong> To help those affected to regain control of their life and face what has happened to them with the fewest possible consequences. Reducing the level of stress produced after the impact of the news or traumatic event. Finally, to connect those affected with their support network.</p>\n<p>There is another <em>Why</em> for this reading though: <strong>Why I am writing about this subject.</strong> The first reason is that <strong>writing is a very effective way to learn.</strong> Besides, I completed a course recently to learn about the topic and be able to help people in these and similar situations. After the course, I wanted to review and share useful knowledge I learned.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Conclusions\" style=\"position:relative;\">Conclusions<a href=\"#Conclusions\" aria-label=\"Conclusions permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/95c6e/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Project Atlantis, cover picture, 1982,  Eberhard Binder.\"\n        title=\"Project Atlantis, cover picture, 1982,  Eberhard Binder.\"\n        src=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/b4294/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/75985/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg 150w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/f93b5/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg 300w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/b4294/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg 600w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/8e1fc/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg 900w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/f1e521423ac9809dd95eb7826feaf176/95c6e/project_atlantis_cover_picture_1982_eberhard_binder.jpg 972w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Project Atlantis, cover picture, 1982,  Eberhard Binder.</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>In the same way as the physical first aid technique, the psychological one can be <strong>decisive to help people</strong> in the first moments they have gone through a tough situation. If we find someone in this situation and apply this technique, we will help them <em>more efficiently.</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"Resources\" style=\"position:relative;\">Resources<a href=\"#Resources\" aria-label=\"Resources permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\" style=\"margin: 0 0 -0.2rem 0.7rem; \"><path fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/a2510/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Hotel in the moon, 1970, Klaus Bürgle.\"\n        title=\"Hotel in the moon, 1970, Klaus Bürgle.\"\n        src=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/b4294/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/75985/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg 150w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/f93b5/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg 300w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/b4294/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg 600w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/8e1fc/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg 900w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/3c5c811263854bc7ee4fc43d92b3f884/a2510/hotel_in_the_moon_1970_klaus_burgle.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Hotel in the moon, 1970, Klaus Bürgle.</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>The majority of the knowledge shared here comes from <a href=\"https://www.coursera.org/learn/pap-covid19\">the course I completed about Psychological First Aid</a>. I have not wanted to extend this article more than necessary, however it also delves into other interesting topics such as <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_stress_disorder\">Acute stress disorder</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post-traumatic_stress_disorder\">Post-traumatic stress disorder</a>, and the relation between each other.</p>\n<p>Other topics explained on it are the famous <strong>Defusing</strong> and <strong>Debriefing</strong> techniques from <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Critical_incident_stress_management\">Critical Incident Stress Management</a>.</p>\n<p>The pictures of the article are related to a recent discovery I made about the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retrofuturism\">Retrofuturism</a> movement. I was amazed by its art and for this article I added the pictures I liked the most from its main artists. The cover picture is <em>The New Universe 76, 1959</em> from <em>Klaus Bürgle.</em></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"What is Psychological First Aid and how to apply it","description":"Key concepts on Psychological First Aid to help people in the immediate aftermath of a disaster","date":"February 18, 2021","tags":["Psychology","Tutorial","Learning","Health"],"commentsUrl":"https://github.com/reymon359/gatsby-personal-site/issues/413","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/gatsby-personal-site/static/f43ad56004888100bc41e60e4f0e9932/2244e/the_new_universe_76_1959_klaus_burgle.jpg"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.2987012987012987,"src":"/gatsby-personal-site/static/f43ad56004888100bc41e60e4f0e9932/f9913/the_new_universe_76_1959_klaus_burgle.jpg","srcSet":"/gatsby-personal-site/static/f43ad56004888100bc41e60e4f0e9932/f836f/the_new_universe_76_1959_klaus_burgle.jpg 200w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/f43ad56004888100bc41e60e4f0e9932/2244e/the_new_universe_76_1959_klaus_burgle.jpg 400w,\n/gatsby-personal-site/static/f43ad56004888100bc41e60e4f0e9932/f9913/the_new_universe_76_1959_klaus_burgle.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/what-is-psychological-first-aid-and-how-to-apply-it/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/basic-tips-for-amateur-star-photography/"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["Adventures","Tutorial","Photography","Canary Islands"],"title":"Basic tips for amateur Star Photography","type":"post"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/traveling-through-the-canary-islands-an-in-depth-guide-to-the-canary-islands/"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["Adventures","Trips","Canary Islands","Guide"],"title":"T